lead_paragraph: Peyton Manning has said Super Bowl 50 could be his "last rodeo" and if the Denver Broncos quarterback rides off into the sunset holding the Vince Lombardi trophy the fairytale finish will not be an unfamiliar one.

headline.print_headline: Last Rodeo or Not, Peyton Assured Spot in Pantheon of Greats
